Text: The Supremes Rule on Nativity Scene in DC jokeSupreme Court has ruled that there cannot be a nativity scene in Washington DC this Christmas This isnt for any religious reason They simply have not been able to find three wise men and a virgin in the Nations capitol There was no problem however finding enough asses to fill the stable Happy Holidays Jim Doering Navigant Consulting Inc

Transwestern Open Season Cc Ladies and Gentlemen In some part due to my influence Transwestern is currently holding an open season to gauge the level of interest in new pipeline capacity to the Phoenix AZ delivery area I assume by now you have seen this news in industry press I encourage each of you to consider the possibility of alternative capacity and the advantages of not being a captive customer to a single pipeline company If you wish to speak directly with the Enron representative or would like to obtain more information please feel free to call Kevin Hyatt at Best Jim This message is being sent blind carbon copy to protect the confidentiality of the recipients James Doering Principal Navigant Consulting Inc Wheeler Road Fourth Floor Burlington MA Phone Fax Cellular
